- Read `docs/spec.md` before architectural refactors.
- Prefer compile-time `html!` macros over runtime template engines (like Tera/Askama).
- Keep dependencies updated using `cargo update`.
- WAF and CSRF middleware are mandatory for all production endpoints.
- Avoid introducing new `unsafe` blocks.
- Ensure all dynamic SQL inputs use parameterization or strict alphanumeric sanitization.
